{"tid":1264724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙報章拒登眾籌廣告，或與加泰問題有關","createTime":"2019-06-28T21:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T13:39:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5b997aad56857864ce76758a0b78e3c739da410f","tid":1264724,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/euobs-media/35c72790b41d77cd7900d8e2ca1e9f70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com%2Feuobs-media%2F35c72790b41d77cd7900d8e2ca1e9f70.jpg&h=ba81375e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以Freedom Hong Kong名義發起的反修例眾籌廣告，在大阪G20期間，已在多國主要報章刊出廣告，包括歐洲的英國和德國，但西班牙的報章卻婉拒刊登。<br />\n<br />\nFreedom Hong Kong表示，對方是以時間所限為由，拒絕刊登他們的公開信。<br />\n<br />\n有從國際版《紐約時報》看到廣告的西班牙讀者指出，事件可能與西班牙國內的加泰羅尼亞問題有關。<br />\n<br />\n加泰地區去年曾經出現百萬人大遊行，要求獨立，但最終得不到西班牙政府回應訴求，部份倡獨領袖更被囚或流亡至國外。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙雖非G20國之一，但屬G20成員歐盟的主要國家，而西班牙語在世界多國均為官方語言，包括G20成員國阿根廷及墨西哥。"},{"pid":"5c261ce7b2e868c939ed2478e2591a6a80a1d950","tid":1264724,"uid":1241,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:32:04.000Z","msg":"歐洲版支那"},{"pid":"dc462db99388dd6cdfab54223fe2d86b153834d3","tid":1264724,"uid":123969,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:33:38.000Z","msg":"下次po加泰報紙<br />\n大家都知對方痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a185c5e0152fca8f986610b12531e8196e12dcf","tid":1264724,"uid":39174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc462db99388dd6cdfab54223fe2d86b153834d3","tid":1264724,"uid":123969,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T21:33:38.000Z","msg":"下次po加泰報紙<br />\n大家都知對方痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T22:05:47.000Z","msg":"同加泰講返you re not alone!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68873420b097081d06ae59fecb6a55f8ad50c344","tid":1264724,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655a15ed5b1dd28762379ec4929fb0aa24c1aab5","tid":1264724,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74edab073e0347ead2d0b843ebfa61124860c42","tid":1264724,"uid":149662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"El Mundo 唔計?"}]}